    "Html": "<p>I'm using Visual Studio 2010 and v2.0 of Chirpy.</p>\n<p>When attempting to combine files in a folder I get the following error:</p>\n<p>\"Error: Pattern attribute required on Folder element. See output window for details.\"</p>\n<p>It's nothing to do with incorrect syntax as the following chirp.config works in v1.0.05 of Chirpy:</p>\n<p>\n<div style=\"color: black; background-color: white;\">\n<pre><span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;?</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">xml</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">version</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.0</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">encoding</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">utf-8</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">?&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">root</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">xmlns:xsi</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">xmlns</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">urn:ChirpyConfig</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">FileGroup</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Name</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">plugin.js</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Minify</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">False</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">&gt;</span>\n        <span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">Folder</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Path</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">plugins</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Type</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">*.js</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Minify</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">true</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">/&gt;</span>       \n    <span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">FileGroup</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">&gt;</span>   \n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">root</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">&gt;</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n</p>",
    "PostedDate": "2011-04-21T08:32:03.083-07:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
  {
    "Id": "601321",
    "ThreadId": "254839",
    "Html": "<p>Chirpy v2 in node \"Folder\" attribute \"Pattern\" is required.</p>\r\n<p>Rename your attribute \"Type\" to \"Pattern\".</p>\r\n<p>Update made by : <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"> <span title=\"Mpdreamz\">Mpdreamz</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><span title=\"Mpdreamz\">changeset : </span></span><a href=\"http://chirpy.codeplex.com/SourceControl/changeset/changes/4e452cc4e671\">http://chirpy.codeplex.com/SourceControl/changeset/changes/4e452cc4e671</a></p>",
